task: Let us solve a page rank problem. Consider the following web pages and their links: A -> B, A -> C, B -> C, C -> A. Calculate the page rank of each page after 20 iterations of the power iteration method. Assume a damping factor of 0.85. Provide the page rank of each page after 20 iterations.
